body:
Wait, Misaki wants to marry Misaka?? Hmm...

All I have to say about this is that the doujin had some nice moments, but art wasnt really that great, but that is besides the problem.
I did enjoy reading, it is just a pity that nhentai doesnt has a button for likes, I didnt enjoy this enough to fav, but with a like I would be able to know that I had read this before, and maybe came back one day. Please implement a like button (dont do a dislike button).
this is how hentai should look in real life
CORRECTION: IN THE CORRECT TRANSLATION SAYS "MASTER TOUMA"
